      "span_text": "Quantitative samples from ARGAU I were collected from the seawater intake at 9 m depth through a pumping system that did not break delicate planktonic organisms (Balestrini et al. 2000) ; qualitative samples from ARGAU I, GEF I and Iceberg II were collected by net with a mesh size of 20 lm, and the samples from Iceberg I were collected from a Phantom DS-2 remote operating vehicle (ROV) [CITATION_1] ).",
